data.description: Embark on an enchanting journey to a rural paradise on this expansive 7-acre property, where your extraordinary visions can come to life. This blank canvas eagerly awaits your creative touch, offering countless potential building sites to craft your dream cooperative living space amidst nature's embrace. As you arrive, you'll be greeted by a cozy and charming existing home that will capture your heart. Step inside and discover airy vaulted ceilings and sleek laminate flooring, creating an inviting atmosphere. The fabulous viewing deck invites you to unwind and immerse yourself in the serenity of your very own oasis, providing a picturesque vantage point to savor the natural wonders that surround you. For outdoor enthusiasts, the nearby Battle Ground Lake State Park calls you to explore its wonders. Dive into a world of excitement as you paddle board, kayak, or take a refreshing swim. Enjoy leisurely strolls with your beloved furry companion, relishing in the harmony of nature. This exceptional opportunity allows you to embrace the ultimate rural lifestyle while still indulging in the modern conveniences you desire. Don't miss the chance to make this rural paradise your own and turn your dreams into reality on this stunning 7-acre canvas.
